Hey - Games are started manually by the Moderator

Now that there is 13, what will happen is that in a morning (maybe tomorrow) the Moderator will do an activity check - all "new" players (less than a few games played) will be kicked out of the game, and sent an email telling them to rejoin
(This is to ensure that people don't just join and never come back)
Then in the evening after the Activity check, the game will start
These games are "real-time" - so 12 hour days, 12 hour nights - and often last up to a week of real world time
so be sure that you are commited to that if you want to play :)
(That's not to say you need to be online talking 12 hours of every day - but you need to be aware that it's not a fast game
